<title>USA: DIGEX secures $27 mln in financing.</title>
<headline>DIGEX secures $27 mln in financing.</headline>
<dateline>BELTSVILLE, Md 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>DIGEX Inc said Friday it completed previously announced financing arrangements for its 1997 capital requirements with long-term capital lease commitments of more than $27 million.</p>
<p>The company said the agreements will be used for ongoing strategic expansion of its Gold Ring national Internet network and Web site management facilities and the addition of managed-router services for its corporate customers.</p>
